reviewText: I can only assume that this a kind of Tabata Light program as the demo models are in no way putting in enough intensity to reach the necessary heart rate levels to access the Tabata back and forth that is supposed to create a lasting fat burning effect.
I love this product. This is really designed for people who are intimidated by gyms like me, or just don't have the time to squeeze in a long workout. It has changed my life.

This is a fantastic workout program. I love exercising but with work and kids don't have much time. These fast and intense workouts keep me in shape better than my prior two hour workouts, I have more energy, and look better.
